,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"小到唔知點洗"},{"pid":"567a38800da2b181cc2c5bd09aa5eb5fb5bb28cf","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捐左佢 代表馬會多謝你</blockquote><br />\n之前講過有定時自動轉帳碑某慈善組織<br />\n唔會賭馬<br />\n捐錢我雖然係捐得少，不過係定時同長期的。多多益善少少無拘，平時都有做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3224c502600c9132cbc003f6525e1b1674cb36e","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小到唔知點洗</blockquote><br />\n巴打一定好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對我學生毒L黎講算幾多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6763455f49721a893f0b004c8f2b72d8a8da57","tid":175050,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"搵10000 仲有10000洗?<br />\n0支出?"},{"pid":"8d09f2ecf977a74f57a14aa449981bcad613abb2","tid":175050,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"叫下雞出下火囉 搵人教你洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a848168eaad337ab7df3060a0e949089cba9a111","tid":175050,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀緊書嘅話就洗哂佢唔好儲，到你出嚟做野有錢冇時間洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">或者冇錢又冇時間</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔到咁多，毒L冇朋友又唔會出街又冇娛樂。只想依家好好利用筆錢將來唔好咁辛苦。多謝巴打意見，有時今朝有酒今朝醉係好嘅</blockquote><br />\n俾我"},{"pid":"4ea77a5016bf79df04292309b1a2f41aedb1fa3f","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫下雞出下火囉 搵人教你洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔叫雞<br />\n我只係想聽下大家意見，唔算係要教洗錢<br />\n而且點用錢都算係學問黎，我冇咁嘅智慧同經驗先上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3ca10b300b40ec53232d2a0103d2cde9a8e50d","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵10000 仲有10000洗?<br />\n0支出?</blockquote><br />\n我已經扣除左平時食野同開支嘅錢，大約有10000蚊"},{"pid":"900e1ebf4eae03cbbe518b15725a87a13c860562","tid":175050,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"月供股票囉"},{"pid":"dff858175eb45b520dfa7d90f7bb6f506703ca28","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da097101bfb78d98af7e2dfcc0d5cfab9540a2c1","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6693f8c5ecc354ad52329aeb0d30030b0f40282e","tid":175050,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:17:37.000Z","msg":"比返老細多謝佢提供就業機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3930e29926e165a5ce156b496a23795065e6dc4c","tid":175050,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 巴打可以唔答<br />\n要做貴價補習係咪要果科5**先得<br />\n同埋你搵咁多都一定多學生 男仔點先易d搵到學生 thanks"},{"pid":"8c2dc495eac7684438a5c372233682ac4e0f1072","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比返老細多謝佢提供就業機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a833e446439e50789da754a465eb8bd3b21d1fa7","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇一問 巴打可以唔答<br />\n要做貴價補習係咪要果科5**先得<br />\n同埋你搵咁多都一定多學生 男仔點先易d搵到學生 thanks</blockquote><br />\n唔一定嘅，不過我果科就五星星同埋係主科黎，教嘅嘢多好多有唔同分卷。<br />\n其實唔多得幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教咁多影響教學質素"},{"pid":"fda7d2ce8ba81dd87dcea3be5efac924e31db052","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dd70cf0cc19523fffe976046a5c3639fac8faf","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83d8b4b49717d599a1eec74900f2fa7e0b508ee","tid":175050,"uid":30950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"其實應該投資自己，學一門手藝語言又好，學一門興趣都好<br />\n<br />\n學生時期算係最多時間，錢第日可以揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c8a795e8a1ad0f15f013999d55aa761cfad98e","tid":175050,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實應該投資自己，學一門手藝語言又好，學一門興趣都好<br />\n<br />\n學生時期算係最多時間，錢第日可以揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學緊日文，不過係為興趣多，將來做嘢應該用唔到<br />\n其實啱，依家都諗住唔做parttime擺多d時間學